ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project is a C-based MP3 metadata editor that allows you to read, validate, and update ID3 tags (like Title, Artist, Album, Year, and Comment) in .mp3 files.
It demonstrates file handling, error checking, and data manipulation in C, making it a great project for embedded systems and systems programming learners.


